attributes.long-description:
The popular puzzle game of Sudoku is brought to the next generation with a variety of new features, enhanced graphics, and animated backgrounds. Go! Sudoku for the PLAYSTATION®3 system is one of the most addictive puzzle games ever, and challenges your mind to solve the puzzles using logic alone.

This Go! Sudoku bundle includes all four puzzle packs for 1200 puzzles in all, catered to both novices and experts alike.

Key Features: • Includes 1200 Puzzles – Contains all four puzzle packs for 1200 sudoku puzzles in all, playable with single and multiplayer challenges and various play modes.
• Multiplayer Battle Mode – Up to 4 players can race to solve a single puzzle board for a challenging, competitive twist. All multiplayer modes are available for online play only.
• Online Rankings – See how you stack up against other players.

Purchase or use of this item is subject to the PlayStation®Network Terms of Service, this item’s use restrictions, and other terms and conditions located at http://www.us.playstation.com/support/useragreements. If you do not wish to accept all these terms, do not purchase or use this item. One-time license fee for downloads to up to 2 console systems that are associated with the purchasing account.
